<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mellotron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.mellotron.com" class="external text" title="http://www.mellotron.com" rel="nofollow">Mellotron.com</a> - US manufacturers and trademark owners</li>
<li><a href="http://mellotronics.com" class="external text" title="http://mellotronics.com" rel="nofollow">Mellotronics.com</a> - Streetly Electronics, UK manufacturers</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mikedickson.org.uk/mellotronworks" class="external text" title="http://www.mikedickson.org.uk/mellotronworks" rel="nofollow">mellotronworks</a> - A free album of Mellotron only music, playing various assorted classical pieces</li>
<li><a href="http://www.planetmellotron.com" class="external text" title="http://www.planetmellotron.com" rel="nofollow">Planet Mellotron.com</a> - List of Mellotron recordings and album reviews</li>
<li><a href="http://www.kleonard.com/mellotron" class="external text" title="http://www.kleonard.com/mellotron" rel="nofollow">Mellotron info and get-togethers</a> - Mellotron Symposia, MONEYPIT, and more</li>
<li><a href="http://www.audities.org" class="external text" title="http://www.audities.org" rel="nofollow">Audities</a> - The home of the Mellotron document and tape archives</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mellotron.fr" class="external text" title="http://www.mellotron.fr" rel="nofollow">Candor Chasma</a> - The main French resource about the Mellotron (English version available)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mellofest.com" class="external text" title="http://www.mellofest.com" rel="nofollow">MelloFest - A new festival celebrating the music of the Mellotron.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IDW5joN0J7U" class="external text" title="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IDW5joN0J7U" rel="nofollow">Video</a> showing Mellotron internal workings and how tape racks can be changed.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.omenie.com/ellatron" class="external text" title="http://www.omenie.com/ellatron" rel="nofollow">Omenie's Ellatron</a> - a UK company's Mellotron-inspired synthesizer for the iPhone</li>
</ul>


